column5: This cottage can be the guest house for the Dome, or it can be rented separately. Shares the pool with the Dome, but never have had a conflict. One king bedroom, queen sleeper sofa, one bath, kitchen, laundry, Sleeps 2-4, pool, patio bistro table and grill. Good dogs ok City of Port Aransas Reg.#(PHONE NUMBER HIDDEN)
column8: Cottage in the Dunes, Pool, Walk to beach!
